ng or commenting on this extension at the official <a target="_blank" href="http://extensions.joomla.org/extensions/social-web/republish/14580">Joomla! Extensions</a> website. This wont take much time !!</li><li><a target="_blank" href="http://www.facebook.com/pages/Like-button-plugin/124895774258192">Like/Follow Us at the official Facebook Like Button Fan page</a> </li></ul><br /><iframe src="http://www.spearheadsoftwares.com/spearhead-facebook-like-current-version?utm_source=fblike_admin&utm_medium=iframe&utm_campaign=product&tmpl=component" frameborder="0" scrolling="no"></iframe>]]></description>
